{"tid":1163263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【中美貿易戰】特朗普：在我任內 中國休想經濟超越美國","createTime":"2019-05-20T10:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T23:17:04.000Z","uid":54733,"like":361,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"5791fd9e012b8494bf915aa4c69541d6e610926f","tid":1163263,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T10:48:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190520/large/1558334036_85eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190520%2Flarge%2F1558334036_85eb.jpg&h=3d817dcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特朗普說，眼下中國經濟並不是很好，「可以我們的經濟一直都非常棒」(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中美貿易戰陰霾籠罩，美國總統特朗普接受《霍士新聞頻道》訪問時指，對中美貿易戰感到「特別高興」（Very happy），還說在他任期內，中國別想成為世界頭號超級大國。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國於本月初上調2,000億美元中國貨關稅，由10%增至25%，及後又將中國科技巨企華為及其子公司列入黑名單。據《彭博》報道，被問及中美貿易戰的結局時，特朗普表示，並不急於與中國重回談判桌，又稱「我們會有數以十億美元計的進賬」，「中國做得顯然不會有我們這麼好」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特朗普說，中國目前經濟並不是很好，但美國經濟一直都非常棒。他指，「中國追趕我們、超越我們。要是希拉莉當總統，中國經濟規模恐怕在她任滿時，就已經遠大於我們，但現在他們連拉近距離都別想。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特朗普表示，中國人雄心壯志，認為中國意圖取代美國成為世界頭號超級大國，但他重申，這樣的事「在我這兒不會發生」。<br />\n<br />\n據國際貨幣基金組織（IMF）2018年各國經濟數據顯示，去年美國GDP及中國GDP分別為20.5萬億美元及13.5萬億美元。匯豐經濟學家去年預計，在2030年，中國GDP將達26萬億美元，成為世界最大經濟體，而美國GDP則會上升至25.2萬億美元。IMF去年亦預期，中國在2030年或成世界上最大的經濟體。"},{"pid":"8cc010e38150accbb874648346d1930d458e222d","tid":1163263,"uid":54733,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T10:48:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190520/59621230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190520%2F59621230&d=RsYziF%2F%2FwXRI7aJQ3s5lGS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=8d9ae7df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190520%2F59621230&h=3f15c44b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190520/59621230</a>"},{"pid":"92c231316691e9f435543c2adba4ff2a7e71b6e4","tid":1163263,"uid":41545,"like":360,"dislike":1,"score":359,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T10:52:19.000Z","msg":"美國係最危急既時刻選左侵侵<br />\n但都要多得美國開國先賢整出呢個選舉制度<br />\n唔係計總票數侵侵係輸左"},{"pid":"06ba5d34f0e0c94bcc38467d0e18711ad8e768b3","tid":1163263,"uid":155095,"like":241,"dislike":1,"score":240,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T10:54:22.000Z","msg":"侵侵再犀利最多做多一屆<br />\n<br />\n習老友終身制佢點比得上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2632406/org/f56296896bb9777f5f00ae88a20abfe8.jpg/Xq1sd6D2pRWDvuiPO5FTZmJ7UQSikefxjZiAB42YgAc?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2632406%2Forg%2Ff56296896bb9777f5f00ae88a20abfe8.jpg%2FXq1sd6D2pRWDvuiPO5FTZmJ7UQSikefxjZiAB42YgAc%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=c5b8b830&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/03184217/612.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F03184217%2F612.png&h=40ca4b26&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0654ef1a43bd5f0aec21b9e58808def1089da87","tid":1163263,"uid":41545,"like":205,"dislike":1,"score":204,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T10:54:57.000Z","msg":"回顧返侵侵頭兩年做既野<br />\n真係令全世界睇穿支那想統治世界既野心同埋幾低劣既手段想浸透全世界<br />\n團結晒兩黨一致抗中"},{"pid":"dd872f1493399fb528b4925e8a7be936628dc877","tid":1163263,"uid":157362,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T10:55:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8bfe2095eec55b61628df914b670f49c40b95fe","tid":1163263,"uid":59898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T10:55:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89649d2eff514ab0740d765f635d58ea1b260a0","tid":1163263,"uid":76310,"like":180,"dislike":2,"score":178,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T10:56:27.000Z","msg":"你真係無得唔服強国<br />\n<br />\n